suite. Accuracy and fidelity to the source matter more than filling every section.

================================================================
A. CORE PRINCIPLE — EXTRACT FAITHFULLY, NEVER FABRICATE
================================================================
- "Exhaustive" means capturing every testable detail that IS in the document — not inventing
